Safran to Propose Single Board Structure, Echos Says

-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 
2011-03-07T11:10:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-07/sanofi-to-propose-adopting-single-board-structure-echos-says.html
(Corrects the company concerned to Safran, not Sanofi-
Aventis SA.)    Safran SA (SAF)  will propose switching to
a single-board governance structure from the current dual-board
system at its shareholder meeting on April 21, French daily Les
Echos reported, citing the company.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  